cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.CY

The paper discusses privacy and security issues in IoT and the use of program analysis techniques to identify these issues. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the analysis of programming platforms, which suggests a possible fit with cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses the implementation of IoT systems, which suggests a possible fit with cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
